"""
Finance API endpoints.

Manual account + valuation CRUD and the service liveness endpoint. Owner
scoping is centralized in the ``get_owner_user_id`` dependency (the caller's
id when auth is present, else ``None``); ownership failures return **404**
(not 403) so a row's existence isn't leaked across users. The outer
``/api/v1`` prefix comes from the router wiring, not from here.
"""

